      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MY MUM MIA (1) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing fifth (23.11) in a Novice race at this track. Won at her only start from this box. Better than the latest effort and deserves another chance. BLOSSOMING FUN (2) missed the frame and was safely held latest finishing 7th at this track following on from a third place finish (23.23) there the start prior. Key runner who gets her chance to atone. LORETTA KEEPING (8) doesn't have the best strike-rate but recent form is sound. Has been in the money the last three starts, the latest when third (23.02) at this track. Goes very well here at the trip finding the frame in each of three starts. Expecting another good run. BOOM BAM SHIFTY (4) cannot be written off despite a miss here at his latest outing.",
